            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Lambertus/Ciaccio">Lamberto</name> detto
                            Ciaccio</persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Bonitius"
                            >Bonizio</name></persName> e la moglie <persName><name ref="Ingitia"
                                >Inghizia </name></persName>del <persName>fu <name ref="Dominicus"
                                >Domenico</name></persName>, con il consenso del marito, interrogata
                        dal <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">giudice del sacro palazzo</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge"><name ref="Sigefredus"
                                >Sighifridi</name></persName>, vendono a <persName><name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lamberto</name></persName> figlio <rs
                            key="#Clerical_concubinage">della <persName key="#Clerical_concubinage"
                                >fu <name ref="Sassa">Sassa</name></persName></rs>, 2 appezzamenti
                        di terra, quod sunt olivetis, posti in loco et finibus <placeName
                            ref="#places/721">Cumpito</placeName> ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/721">Petra Spendurla</placeName>: il primo <rs
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions">confinante</rs> uno capo con terra
                        della <rs key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di <orgName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/242">San Pietro qui dicitur Maiore</orgName>,
                        alio capo con terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Iocus">Ioco</name></persName> et de suis consortibus, lato uno
                        con terra del <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Priests"><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Savinus"
                                >Savino</name></persName>, alio lato con terra di <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Mencuccius"
                                >Mencuccio</name></persName> e con terra di <persName
                            key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Morectus"
                            >Moretto</name></persName>; il secondo confinante ambas capitas cum uno
                        lato con terra de <rs key="#Hospitals">ospitale</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3101">Sancte Marie</orgName>, alio lato con
                        terra di <persName key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions"><name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martino</name></persName>, ricevendo da <persName><name
                                ref="Blancardus">Blancardo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name
                                ref="Paganus">Pagano</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Meritum/launechild #Jewels">meritum anulo aureo</rs> pro 31 soldi.
                        Chiedono al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Ildebrandus"
                            >Ildebrando</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer #Judge"
                                ><name ref="Sigefredus">Sighifridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer #Judge">iudex sacri palatii</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Rigitius">Righizio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Andreas">Andrea</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus">Gherardo</name></persName> di
                                <persName><name ref="Cicco">Cigo</name></persName>.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
